{"version": 2, "width": 90, "height": 36, "timestamp": 1776706075, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "AI-Drift Firewall — Agent-Time Gate"}
[0.004097, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[1.006079, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[0;36m  AI-Drift Firewall — Agent-Time Hook\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Wykrywanie architektury w czasie generowania kodu\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Platforma : Claude Code (PreToolUse hook)\r\n"]
[1.006147, "o", "  Reguły    : CYCLE_NEW · LAYER_VIOLATION · BOUNDARY_LEAK\r\n  Latencja  : ~350ms per edit\r\n"]
[4.008882, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.008963, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m  Architektura serwisu (src/)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n    domain/          ← czyste value objects, zero I/O\r\n    application/     ← orkiestracja, zależy od domain\r\n    infrastructure/  ← adaptery bazy danych, SMTP itp.\r\n    payments_api/    ← jedyna autoryzowana brama do payments_core\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mReguła: domain NIE może importować infrastructure\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mReguła: domain NIE może tworzyć cyklu z application\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.011805, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  KROK 1/3 — Czysty baseline\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[2m  $ cat src/domain/order.py\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[9.516655, "o", "\"\"\"Order value object — pure domain, no infrastructure dependencies.\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\r\n\r\n\r\n@dataclass(frozen=True)\r\nclass Order:\r\n    id: str\r\n    customer_id: str\r\n    total_cents: int\r\n\r\n    def validate(self) -> None:\r\n        if self.total_cents < 0:\r\n            raise ValueError(\"total_cents must be non-negative\")\r\n"]
[12.519009, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[0;32m✓ Zero naruszeń. Czysty DAG.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.520406, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  KROK 2/3 — AI agent dodaje forbidden import\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Scenariusz: agent \"helpfully\" optymalizuje kod\r\n  i dodaje bezpośredni import do infrastructure.db\r\n\r\n"]
[18.523471, "o", "\u001b[2m  ── Proponowana zmiana: ───────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;31m+ from src.infrastructure.db import save\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;31m+ save(self)  # persist directly from domain\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[21.526338, "o", "\u001b[1;33m  [PreToolUse hook] → skanowanie propozycji…\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[23.118577, "o", "qse-gate: blocked — this change would introduce a structural violation.\r\n\r\n  [CYCLE_NEW] src.domain.order → src.infrastructure.db\r\n    axiom: acyclicity (MDL: cycle increases graph description length; flow: bidirectional information transport blurs module boundaries)\r\n    fix:   Extract a shared interface to break the cycle, or invert one dependency via dependency injection.\r\n  [LAYER_VIOLATION] src.domain.order → src.infrastructure.db\r\n    axiom: layering (MDL: high-level layer compressed independently of low-level; flow: information must not flow inward to core)\r\n    fix:   Define a port/interface in domain that infrastructure implements. Depend on the port, not the concrete.\r\n"]
[24.129965, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[0;31m\u001b[1m✗ ZABLOKOWANO (exit 2)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mClaude widzi naruszenie aksjomatu i poprawia kod.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[28.132633, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  KROK 3/3 — AI agent zamyka cykl zależności\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  Scenariusz: agent dodaje wygodny import w odwrotnym kierunku\r\n  domain.order → application.order_service → (powrót do domain)\r\n\r\n"]
[31.135617, "o", "\u001b[2m  ── Proponowana zmiana: ───────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;31m+ from src.application.order_service import notify\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[34.138398, "o", "\u001b[1;33m  [PreToolUse hook] → skanowanie propozycji…\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[35.736669, "o", "qse-gate: blocked — this change would introduce a structural violation.\r\n\r\n  [CYCLE_NEW] src.application.order_service → src.domain.order\r\n    axiom: acyclicity (MDL: cycle increases graph description length; flow: bidirectional information transport blurs module boundaries)\r\n    fix:   Extract a shared interface to break the cycle, or invert one dependency via dependency injection.\r\n  [LAYER_VIOLATION] src.domain.order → src.application.order_service\r\n    axiom: layering (MDL: high-level layer compressed independently of low-level; flow: information must not flow inward to core)\r\n    fix:   Define a port/interface in domain that application implements. Depend on the port, not the concrete.\r\n"]
[36.748178, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[0;31m\u001b[1m✗ ZABLOKOWANO (exit 2)\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mCykl wykryty. Aksjom acykliczności naruszony.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[40.751024, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  BONUS — Czysty zapis (brak naruszeń)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;33m  [PreToolUse hook] → skanowanie propozycji…\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[42.361428, "o", "\u001b[0;32m\u001b[1m  ✓ PRZEPUSZCZONO — brak output, brak blokady\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[46.363083, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m  Podsumowanie\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  LAYER_VIOLATION (domain → infrastructure)   \u001b[0;31mZABLOKOWANO\u001b[0m\r\n  CYCLE_NEW (domain ↔ application)            \u001b[0;31mZABLOKOWANO\u001b[0m\r\n  Czysty zapis                                \u001b[0;32mPRZEPUSZCZONO\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mLatencja:  ~350ms  |  Czytelność: aksjom + hint naprawy\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mHook aktywny dla każdego Edit/Write w Claude Code\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[46.363158, "o", "\u001b[2m  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
